text: We Two may refer to: * "We two," a personal pronoun in certain languages (See "we".) * We two, ours one, a population planning term. * Vi två, a 1939 Swedish film directed by Schamyl Bauman. * We Two Alone, a 1952 Italian comedy film. * "We Two," a 1983 song by the Little River Band, released in The Net album. * We Two Are One Too, a 1990 music compilation video released by the British pop group Eurythmics. * We Two Kings, a 2002 episode of tenth season of Frasier.
title: We Two
